properties.sfomuseum:description: Passenger ticket and ticket jacket issued by Western Airlines,  serial number 017:100:844:704; to passenger Stanford Horn, Los Angeles to San Francisco; dates of use: November 29 - December 8, 1963;a. ticket; white and red cover with route map; $14.18 fare for flight 466 on December 8, 1963; missing two coupons.b. ticket jacket and gate pass; blue, white, and red cover; text "Flight 631, Destination LAS (Las Vegas) Gate 37, Coach" on back.
